      'px (pixels)',
      'Absolute units: px (pixels), pt (points), pc (picas), in (inches), cm (centimeters), mm (millimeters). Relative units: em, rem, %, vw, vh, vmin, vmax, ch, ex. Absolute units don''t scale with user preferences.',
