      'fr distributes available space proportionally; % is fixed relative to container',
      '''fr'' (fraction) distributes available space proportionally. <code>1fr</code> <code>2fr</code> means second column gets twice the space. Percentages are fixed relative to container. ''fr'' is more flexible for responsive grids. Use ''fr'' for flexible columns, % for fixed proportions.',
