    ),
    (
      gen_random_uuid(),
      'Explain the Content Security Policy (CSP) meta tag and how it prevents XSS attacks. What are the key directives?',
      'Security is critical for senior developers. How does CSP work, what directives are most important, and how does it prevent XSS?',
      'multiple-choice',
      'advanced',
      20,
      '[{"id":"o1","text":"CSP restricts resource loading sources, preventing XSS by blocking unauthorized scripts/styles. Key directives: default-src, script-src, style-src","isCorrect":true,"explanation":"Correct. CSP is a security mechanism that whitelists allowed sources for resources, preventing injection attacks."},{"id":"o2","text":"CSP only prevents clickjacking, not XSS attacks","isCorrect":false,"explanation":"Incorrect. CSP primarily prevents XSS by controlling script execution. X-Frame-Options prevents clickjacking."},{"id":"o3","text":"CSP allows all inline scripts by default for convenience","isCorrect":false,"explanation":"Incorrect. CSP blocks inline scripts by default. ''unsafe-inline'' must be explicitly added, but it reduces security."},{"id":"o4","text":"CSP is only needed for sites with user-generated content","isCorrect":false,"explanation":"Incorrect. CSP should be used on all sites as defense-in-depth, not just sites with user content."}]',
      'CSP restricts resource loading sources, preventing XSS by blocking unauthorized scripts/styles. Key directives: default-src, script-src, style-src',
      'CSP restricts which resources (scripts, styles, images) can be loaded and executed, preventing XSS by blocking inline scripts and unauthorized sources. Key directives: default-src (fallback), script-src (JavaScript sources), style-src (CSS sources), img-src (images), connect-src (AJAX/fetch). ''unsafe-inline'' and ''unsafe-eval'' should be avoided when possible.',
      NULL,
      ARRAY['Think about how XSS attacks inject malicious scripts', 'Consider what ''whitelist'' vs ''blacklist'' means for security', 'Remember that CSP is a defense-in-depth strategy'],
      ARRAY['html', 'security', 'csp', 'xss', 'difficult'],
      '{}',
      NULL,
